snippet.title: NEW YORK, NY - APRIL 27: Models pose at a fashion shoot for W Magazine on April 27, 2012 in New York City. PUBLISHED IMAGE. Shoes from left: Yves Saint Laurent, Celine, Fendi, Balenciaga by Nicolas Ghesquiere. On model: Barlette and bottoms by Zinke. CREDIT MUST READ: Santiago & Mauricio/Contour Style. (Photo by Santiago Sierra/Contour Style by Getty Images)

PARIS, FRANCE - JANUARY 01: Model poses at a fashion shoot for Madame Figaro in 2009 in Paris, France. Published image. Figaro ID#: 085089-009. Jacket by Yves Saint Laurent, jumper by Paul & Joe, boots by Pataugas. CREDIT MUST READ: Florian Claudel/Figarophoto/Contour Style. (Photo by Florian Claudel/Figarophoto/Contour Style by Getty Images)

PARIS, FRANCE - AUGUST 01: Model poses at a fashion shoot for Madame Figaro on August 1, 2011 in Paris, France. Published image. Figaro ID#: 101355-007. Boots by Guy Laroche, fur coat and bag by Salvatore Ferragamo, dress by Yves Saint Laurent, cuff by Patrick Moulin. CREDIT MUST READ: Frederic Farre/Figarophoto/Contour Style. (Photo by Frederic Farre/Figarophoto/Contour Style by Getty Images)

PARIS, FRANCE - SEPTEMBER 10: Models pose at a fashion shoot for Madame Figaro on September 10, 2003 in Paris, France. Published image. Figaro ID#: 059898-003. Pants by Naf Naf, small bag by Tom Ford for Yves Saint Laurent Rive Gauche, shoes by Minelli, skirt by Kookai, stockings by Gerbe, bag by Lamarthe, boots by Mine de Rien. CREDIT MUST READ: Fabrice Cormy/Figarophoto/Contour Style. (Photo by Fabrice Cormy/Figarophoto/Contour Style by Getty Images)

A model poses for a fashion shoot in Paris, 2008. Outfit and shoes by Yves Saint Laurent, purse by Dior, bag by Longchamp. Figaro ID #: 081968-007. Published image. CREDIT MUST READ: Philippe Biancotto/Figarophoto/Contour Style

PARIS, FRANCE - JULY 19: Model poses at a fashion shoot for Madame Figaro on July 19, 2011 in Paris, France. Figaro ID#: 101444-012. Pants, jacket, shirt and boots by Gucci, ring by Marc by Marc Jacobs, bag by Yves Saint Laurent. CREDIT MUST READ: Naomi Yang/Figarophoto/Contour Style. (Photo by Naomi Yang/Figarophoto/Contour Style by Getty Images)

PARIS, FRANCE - JULY 13: Model poses at a fashion shoot for Madame Figaro on July 13, 2011 in Paris, France. Published image. Figaro ID#: 101460-010. Jacket by Maje, fur vest by Milady, turtleneck by Petit Bateau, leggings and belt by Gerard Darel, bracelet by Yves Saint Laurent, bag by Prada, boots by Giuseppe Zanotti Design. CREDIT MUST READ: Lise-Anne Marsal/Figarophoto/Contour Style. (Photo by Lise-Anne Marsal/Figarophoto/Contour Style by Getty Images)
